<p>She was born in 1977 in Istanbul. She completed her primary, secondary, high school and university education in Istanbul. She lived abroad for many years and worked in the gastronomy and aviation industry. Since her return to Turkey in 2013, she has been working as a manager in the field of international trade in the private sector. Her volunteering activities started in childhood with her family. She continues to voluntarily support many foundations and associations, especially the Sen De Gel Association, in order to be beneficial to the society and the environment.</p>